Rating: 3
This is an excellent dessert, but very rich. I made it to follow a light meal with a main dish salad (lobster,pink grapefruit and avocado salad from this site.) The coconut shortbread cookies (and the creme fraiche) are essential to the overall decadence of the dish. I don't care much for bananas but even I loved this dessert!